00:39:24.100 --> 00:39:26.700 align:middle line:84%
So one thing is that
you try to prove it.

00:39:26.700 --> 00:39:30.680 align:middle line:84%
Another thing is that you try
to explain to other the proof.

00:39:30.680 --> 00:39:36.980 align:middle line:84%
And so in either case, if you
can divide it into substeps--

00:39:36.980 --> 00:39:42.660 align:middle line:84%
