00:48:45.230 --> 00:48:52.930 align:middle line:90%


00:48:52.930 --> 00:48:56.850 align:middle line:90%
Each is closed non-empty.

00:48:56.850 --> 00:49:08.610 align:middle line:84%
And the family or
