00:59:53.150 --> 00:59:59.350 align:middle line:84%
And let's say that
this is y3, whatever.

00:59:59.350 --> 01:00:01.050 align:middle line:90%
So there's infinitely many n's.

01:00:01.050 --> 01:00:03.990 align:middle line:90%


01:00:03.990 --> 01:00:08.430 align:middle line:84%
So now, I can just think
about that one ball.

01:00:08.430 --> 01:00:12.220 align:middle line:84%
