01:00:54.610 --> 01:01:11.220 align:middle line:90%


01:01:11.220 --> 01:01:15.300 align:middle line:84%
OK, now, I want to somehow
repeat this process.

01:01:15.300 --> 01:01:17.700 align:middle line:90%
