the right radii

01:01:30.660 --> 01:01:34.796 align:middle line:90%
has to use over and over again.

01:01:34.796 --> 01:01:40.200 align:middle line:84%
And so I want to
repeat this process.

01:01:40.200 --> 01:01:44.220 align:middle line:84%
And for that, I
need to remind you

01:01:44.220 --> 01:01:49.440 align:middle line:84%
that if you take a metric space,
if you have a metric space,

01:01:49.440 --> 01:02:11.010 align:middle line:84%
so recall that if X
here is a metric space,

01:02:11.010 --> 01:02:14.690 align:middle line:90%
A here is a subset--

01:02:14.690 --> 01:02:16.120 align:middle line:90%
is a compact subset.

01:02:16.120 --> 01:02:24.770 align:middle line:90%


01:02:24.770 --> 01:02:40.570 align:middle line:84%
A is a compact subset, and B
here is a closed subset of X.

01:02:40.570 --> 01:02:48.170 align:middle line:84%
Well then A intersected
with B. If it's compact,

01:02:48.170 --> 01:02:51.490 align:middle line:90%
it's also closed.

01:02:51.490 --> 01:02:53.410 align:middle line:90%
We proved that.

01:02:53.410 --> 01:02:56.630 align:middle line:84%
And so this is the intersection
of two closed sets.

01:02:56.630 --> 01:02:58.250 align:middle line:90%
So this is closed.

01:02:58.250 --> 01:03:00.610 align:middle line:90%
This is contained in A.

01:03:00.610 --> 01:03:04.890 align:middle line:84%
And now we proved last
time that if you take--

01:03:04.890 --> 01:03:07.300 align:middle line:90%
so this here is a closed subset.

01:03:07.300 --> 01:03:07.930 align:middle line:90%
This is closed.

01:03:07.930 --> 01:03:11.000 align:middle line:90%


01:03:11.000 --> 01:03:15.140 align:middle line:84%
And it's contained in
A. Since A is compact,

01:03:15.140 --> 01:03:19.700 align:middle line:84%
if you take a closed subset of
A, then this is also compact,

01:03:19.700 --> 01:03:21.790 align:middle line:90%
so this is also compact.

01:03:21.790 --> 01:03:29.040 align:middle line:90%


01:03:29.040 --> 01:03:37.560 align:middle line:84%
So now let's continue
that string of thoughts

01:03:37.560 --> 01:03:39.040 align:middle line:90%
from over there.

01:03:39.040 --> 01:03:43.910 align:middle line:90%
So now we repeat this.

01:03:43.910 --> 01:03:48.280 align:middle line:90%


01:03:48.280 --> 01:03:52.440 align:middle line:90%
So I have a set.

01:03:52.440 --> 01:03:54.880 align:middle line:84%
Maybe I should draw
