01:05:12.730 --> 01:05:22.880 align:middle line:84%
so I'm covering this-- so
cover this by balls of radius.

01:05:22.880 --> 01:05:27.430 align:middle line:90%


01:05:27.430 --> 01:05:29.870 align:middle line:90%
r over 4.

01:05:29.870 --> 01:05:33.870 align:middle line:84%
So I'm going to write this
thing here in the same way.

01:05:33.870 --> 01:05:36.540 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to write this--
this here, I now know--

01:05:36.540 --> 01:05:44.710 align:middle line:90%


01:05:44.710 --> 01:05:48.010 align:middle line:84%
I'm only interested in things
that are contained in A.

01:05:48.010 --> 01:05:51.750 align:middle line:84%
