01:07:58.970 --> 01:08:07.140 align:middle line:90%


01:08:07.140 --> 01:08:08.680 align:middle line:90%
Why finitely many?

01:08:08.680 --> 01:08:10.600 align:middle line:90%
This is because this is compact.

01:08:10.600 --> 01:08:14.900 align:middle line:84%
I'm writing this here as the
