01:08:18.220 --> 01:08:22.600 align:middle line:84%
And so I have the finitely many
of those covered by compactness.

01:08:22.600 --> 01:08:25.974 align:middle line:90%


01:08:25.974 --> 01:08:31.260 align:middle line:84%
And so now what I observe, is
